{
  "stem": "7069.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- tell you what-- this kind of-- that I could do this kind of work rather than working in stone quarries or digging ditches 10, 12 hours was much, much-- was as much worth as extra food, because I could-- in effect, it was like extra food.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, as I say, I could space the use of calories a little bit that way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother kept working on for a while in those, in the field like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, eventually, I was able to get him to work with me in the workshop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that worked out fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Theresienstadt actually was one of the-- not one of the, was the-- artist concentration camp, was all the camps that were in existence.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hitler had earmarked this camp to show the world-- when he, when he knew that people found out that Jews were picked up and sent to concentration camps-- to show the world what a wonderful life these Jews have.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, while they are losing their freedom, but they have freedom within that compound to do most wonderful things that even the German people and, and their German guards couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, steadily, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw them all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and also rabbis, as the clergy-- he sent the famous clergy-- were specifically sent there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had planned to show the world-- and I quote unquote, that's what he said-- 'the town that Hitler gave to the Jews.' And so what I didn't know at the time-- I might just as well first say-- that, that many of these things were secretly filmed.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these artists were not only allowed, they were urged to take advantage of the allowances that, that, that we were-- that, that they can assemble and perform their arts.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
